Pre-Game Insights: England would not be reading too much into the performance, especially because the English are short of T20I experience as compared to the Aussies. They would be keen on bettering their performance this time around.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Sophia Gardens is a venue not commonly used as far as international cricket is concerned. Out of the nine T20Is played here, six have been won by the team chasing. More of the same is expected as the team winning the toss is more than likely to have a bowl first.
Others: Travis Head is considered one of the most fierce strikers of the cricket ball out there.
Adam Zampa has been on a wicket-taking spree on every occasion he has stepped onto the field.
